{"surahDetails":{"id":104,"arabicName":"الهمزة","banglaName":"পরনিন্দাকারী","englishName":"The Traducer","enTranslatedName":"Al-Humazah","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/104.mp3","totalAyah":9},"surah":{"id":104,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","bangl_text":"প্রত্যেক পশ্চাতে ও সম্মুখে পরনিন্দাকারীর দুর্ভোগ","english_text":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6180.mp3","colorText":"وَيْ[u:12392[لٌ ل]ِّكُلِّ هُمَزَ[u:14633[ةٍ ل]ُّمَزَةٍ","juz":30,"ruku":546,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَيْ<span class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>لٌ ل</span>ِّكُلِّ هُمَزَ<span class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ةٍ ل</span>ُّمَزَةٍ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"যে অর্থ সঞ্চিত করে ও গণনা করে","english_text":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6181.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَال[a:14634[اً و]َعَدَّدَهُۥ","juz":30,"ruku":546,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَال<span class=idgham_ghunnah>اً و</span>َعَدَّدَهُۥ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"সে মনে করে যে, তার অর্থ চিরকাল তার সাথে থাকবে","english_text":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6182.mp3","colorText":"يَحْسَبُ أَ[g[نّ]َ مَالَهُ[o[ۥٓ] أَخْلَدَهُۥ","juz":30,"ruku":546,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"يَحْسَبُ أَ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َ مَالَهُ<span class=madda_obligatory>ۥٓ</span> أَخْلَدَهُۥ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","bangl_text":"কখনও না, সে অবশ্যই নিক্ষিপ্ত হবে পিষ্টকারীর মধ্যে।","english_text":"No! He wil